          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The coordinates in the point structure returned by this method are in the range 0.0 to 1.0. The point (0.0, 0.0) corresponds to the top-left corner of the unrotated picture and the point (1.0, 1.0) represents the bottom-right corner of the unrotated picture. "
